==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tamaric
<hw>Tam"a*ric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tamarice</ets>. See <er>Tamarisk</er>.]</ety> <def>A shrub or tree
supposed to be the tamarisk, or perhaps some kind of heath.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He shall be like <qex>tamaric</qex> in the desert, and he shall
not see when good shall come.</q> <rj><qau>Jer. xvii. 6 (Douay
version).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tamarin</ent>⟦br⟧
